<h4 class="release-note release-note__new">NEW</h4>

* [function_rc](/api-reference/liquid/platformos-tags#function) - a new tag to make it easy to store a "result" of a partial in a variable; `rc` stands for release candidate as this is an experimental feature and eventually these tags will be renamed to `function` and `return`
* [hash_assign](/api-reference/liquid/platformos-tags#hash_assign) - a new tag to make it easy to extend a Hash object - syntax sugar for the [add_hash_key](/api-reference/liquid/platformos-filters#add_hash_key-aliases-assign_to_hash_key) filter

